blackengine.gameLogic

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • blackengine.gameLogic.Entity

  • public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    An instance of this class represents an entity in 3D space. This entity can consist of multiple other child entities and components for itself. #Tested

      • addChild

        public void addChild(Entity child)
              throws DuplicateEntityNameException
        Adds a child entity to this entity. If one with the same name was already present, a DuplicateEntityNameException will be thrown. If the parent entity was flagged active, the child will be activated as well.
        Parameters:
        child - An entity that will be added to this entity as a child.
        Throws:
        DuplicateEntityNameException
